{"tid":1317551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[純分享]今日終於連老豆都問我點上連登","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T05:08:40.000Z","uid":247905,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5f60bf72a64657204cbcdcafcca6bc59e9b0741a","tid":1317551,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"覺得無聊可以唔洗推，推返正經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夜晚一齊睇Now新聞，平時睇開TVB，立法會投過葉劉既老豆突然問我：「其實一直想知依班後生係邊到討論可以做到咁有team work？佢地真係好勁好值得支持」<br />\n跟住教佢dl app上咩台咩台，可以起底點分邊個係人邊個係鬼，咩係P牌三毛果D等等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開post目的只係想大家諗下有機會就啟發下身邊老人家緊貼年輕人既諗法，我老豆依家就係與青年同行we connect 喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾驚佢問埋我有無acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然我最後教返佢上香討同BK啦，果邊先係反中亂港大本營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nI love you Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbbed962f793e455fdb72530165fd8afe10e263","tid":1317551,"uid":154293,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:28:41.000Z","msg":"如果自己屋企果個都係咁你話幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b0e8a7ebd97510a30ecc362b6caa01ea39dcde","tid":1317551,"uid":247905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bcbbed962f793e455fdb72530165fd8afe10e263","tid":1317551,"uid":154293,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:28:41.000Z","msg":"如果自己屋企果個都係咁你話幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:31:37.000Z","msg":"或者由電視開始？<br />\n我都係由食飯時間TVB新聞立即轉台去Now新聞開始啟發兩老<br />\n傳媒威力是不容忽視的"},{"pid":"08c489a85f066e0af294403a8cfcc59da8643259","tid":1317551,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:32:57.000Z","msg"